Sub21: Independently-contolled for and aft ballast tank system
Overview
Sub21 is a submarine control system for dual-ballast tank model submarines. Independently-controlled for and aft ballast tanks more closely mimic real submarines.

Dive Technology



Benefits of independently-controlled for and aft ballast tanks
Allow model submarines to more closely mimic real submarines during diving and surfacing manoeuvres. 
Allow user to level submarine without having to add/remove weights.
Allow user to trim submaring without having to add/remove weights.


